{"tid":2240533,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發明左個裝置幫人獲得充足睡眠","createTime":"2020-10-12T16:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T14:06:16.000Z","uid":372785,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6a49fd682af923db3fd476922aaa4810bf6fc1","tid":2240533,"uid":372785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:59:16.000Z","msg":"香港人生活壓力龐大 好難得可以訓得足夠<br />\n好多人日日都訓唔夠8個鍾<br />\n<br />\n喺放假得閒訓教嘅時候<br />\n好多人又唔知點解又好易無啦啦醒左<br />\n之後又訓唔返<br />\n所以想補眠都冇得補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNk6LDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNk6LDy.png&h=2c7c8a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺平日<br />\n好多人都成晚覺唔着教<br />\n只係靠安眠藥先至訓到<br />\n咁樣實在太唔健康喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我發明左個裝置幫人獲得充足睡眠<br />\n希望可以幫到香港人訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1tDBJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1tDBJg.png&h=01b7136b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係我發明既鬧鐘<br />\n佢就有4條帶<br />\n用黎綁住啲手手腳腳<br />\n<br />\n好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvxMLDY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvxMLDY.png&h=546b341e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣用家就唔會喺張床轉嚟轉去<br />\n一訓就可以覺天光<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrN5gNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrN5gNN.png&h=9ea4f0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁夠鐘醒就點算呢？<br />\n佢個鬧鐘夠鐘嘅時候<br />\n就會自己鬆開<br />\n咁就唔會話醒唔到了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5eSGfy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5eSGfy.png&h=a1535ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫大家訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb80701cdf273604155a8751ddc8a66ff597a8e","tid":2240533,"uid":183576,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"好有SM風味"},{"pid":"833fdf893a26a8e3b4655306e37d81a8a0ea9712","tid":2240533,"uid":81692,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"精神病院果d 人都係差唔多"},{"pid":"b2a54e1cf7acd00b6023ec77a856fa41d015569d","tid":2240533,"uid":128705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"但凡半夜急尿肚痾火燭入賊入屋都好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfd02d1a4cc6bcc753061caaa40c8f6163111bb","tid":2240533,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但凡半夜急尿肚痾火燭<span class=\"red\">有</span>賊入屋都好精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268af2afeef3b1019f4741ca1c40cb048fd3e12f","tid":2240533,"uid":28626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得唔轉就一定瞓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d69ab2c19b6c47cf94d297e5fb07ee1827fedf","tid":2240533,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n㩒㩒㩒 㩒你老母咩㩒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c689d3eaa043d7a9e37a5f9303d89003541b366e","tid":2240533,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"805954af5c87b70d23828ecf85d4415e9fae08c8","tid":2240533,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"整部自動隊屎眼機仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgm